high_descs: Go around to the kitchen island to the counter with a toaster and a microwave.
Pick up the gray knife laying perpendicular to the spatula on the counter.
Turn left to go to the front of the refrigerator.
Cut the apple inside the refrigerator into three parts.
Turn right and go to the front of the microwave.
Place the gray knife inside the microwave.
Turn left and go back to the front of the refrigerator.
Take out one piece of the apple from the refrigerator.
Turn left to go to the left side of the sink.
Wash the apple inside the sink under running water and take it out.
Turn around and go back to the front of the microwave.
Place the washed apple piece in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put washed apple piece inside the microwave next to the gray knife.

high_descs: Walk around the room to the left and turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and walk forward and turn right to face the fridge.
Cut the apple in the fridge into three slices.
Turn right and walk across the room and turn left to face the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Turn to the left and walk forward to face the fridge on the right.
Pick up the piece of apple in the fridge.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the sink.
Wash the piece of apple in the sink and then remove it.
Walk to the opposite corner of the room to face the microwave.
Place the piece of apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: TO wash a piece of apple and place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Go towards the counter
Pick up the butterknife on the counter
Go to the fridge
Open the fridge and cut the apple in the fridge
Go to the microwave
Put the butterknife in the microwave
Go to the fridge
Take a cut apple piece out of the fridge
Go to the sink
Wash the apple piece in the sink
Go to the microwave
Put the apple piece in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put a cut and washed apple piece in a microwave
